00:27:49,260 --> 00:27:50,890
My brother-in-law and sister-in-law.

391
00:27:52,820 --> 00:27:53,750
Stop that nonsense.

392
00:27:55,150 --> 00:27:56,080
Come on.

393
00:27:56,210 --> 00:27:57,180
Have a seat here.

394
