and had doubts about us long ago,

412
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:50,370
then could it be possible

413
00:28:50,460 --> 00:28:52,310
that he was lying about Spectre

414
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:53,450
coming to Yungang?

415
00:28:53,940 --> 00:28:56,440
