650
00:40:56,170 --> 00:40:57,230
What is it?

651
00:40:57,840 --> 00:41:00,480
I thought she was a spoiled brat.

652
00:41:00,790 --> 00:41:01,850
I didn't expect

653
00:41:02,290 --> 00:41:03,870
