00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:10,600
It's not strange.

657
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:14,210
You've always been terrible at art.

658
00:41:16,280 --> 00:41:17,470
If you keep saying that,

659
00:41:17,560 --> 00:41:18,520
I'll stop telling.

